      "date": "2014-01-14 18:34:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nJ-C: positive/1 value is a specific return value from mgs_modify() that seem to indicate that \"no modification occured because not necessary\" … It is not clear for me what you would like me to add, only to comment/highlight this in mgs_modify() comments/header ?\n\nJames: I detailled how mgs_setparam() can return 1 in my inlined comment. Do you meant that you want me to test it explicitelly instead of >0 ?",
